/* Program to Replace All Occurrences of a Character *\

public class ReplaceAllOccurrences {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        String input = "Java Programming";
        char charToReplace = 'a';  // Character to replace
        char replacementChar = 'o';  // Character to replace with
        
        // Replace all occurrences of 'a' with 'o'
        String result = input.replace(charToReplace, replacementChar);

        System.out.println("Original String: " + input);
        System.out.println("String after replacement: " + result);
    }
}
Output:
Original String: Java Programming
String after replacement: Jovo Progromming

Explanation:
replace(char oldChar, char newChar) replaces all occurrences of oldChar in the string with newChar.
